description: One more win sends Texas Tech from San Diego to San Francisco. Standing in the way of a trip to the Sweet 16 up the California coastline, a team from South Bend, Indiana.Â The third-seeded Red Raiders (26-9) take on 11th-seeded Notre Dame (24-10) at 4:10 p.m. (PT) in the NCAA Tournament Second Round at the Viejas Arena on the San Diego State University campus.
